\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 can be written as 
\begin_inset Formula $4k$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $4k+1$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $4k+2$
\end_inset

, or 
\begin_inset Formula $4k+3$
