\begin_inset Formula $x\in\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $4\mid\left(x^{4}-x^{2}\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
We directly suppose that 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

.
